3
00:02:04,730 --> 00:02:05,520
[thud]

4
00:02:05,520 --> 00:02:07,190
– [SAILOR A] Huh?
– [SAILOR B] Huh?

5
00:02:14,700 --> 00:02:15,160
[SAILOR grunts]

6
00:02:16,780 --> 00:02:19,410
Ugh. I missed again.

7
00:02:18,030 --> 00:02:19,410
[SAILOR A laughs]

8
00:02:19,410 --> 00:02:20,700
Strike three, pal.

9
00:02:20,700 --> 00:02:22,250
[SAILOR C]
I'd be embarrassed.

10
00:02:22,250 --> 00:02:23,870
You suck!

11
00:02:25,250 --> 00:02:25,880
Hm?

12
00:02:30,460 --> 00:02:33,010
[SAILOR B grunts]
It's heavier than I thought it'd be!

13
00:02:33,010 --> 00:02:34,260
Maybe it's filled with beer!

14
00:02:34,260 --> 00:02:36,340
[SAILOR A grunts]
Well, I think it's our beer now.

15
00:02:36,340 --> 00:02:39,310
[whimpering]

16
00:02:42,480 --> 00:02:44,440
[menacing orchestral music]

17
00:02:47,270 --> 00:02:49,070
Ship off the starboard bow!

18
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:50,530
[SAILORS A & B]
Huh?

19
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:51,480
[SAILOR C]
And they're flying a pirate flag!

20
00:02:51,480 --> 00:02:53,610
We've got a pirate ship in pursuit!

21
00:02:53,610 --> 00:02:55,610
Enemy raid! Enemy raid!

22
00:02:53,950 --> 00:02:55,610
[SAILOR A & B scream]

23
00:02:56,780 --> 00:02:58,370
[cannon fire]

24
00:03:04,540 --> 00:03:07,000
[PASSENGERS screaming]

25
00:03:19,350 --> 00:03:20,890
[ALVIDA]
Koby!

26
00:03:20,890 --> 00:03:22,220
Yes, ma'am?

27
00:03:22,220 --> 00:03:25,640
[ALVIDA] Who is the most beautiful
of all on these seas?

28
00:03:23,890 --> 00:03:24,560
[KOBY] Uh...

29
00:03:25,640 --> 00:03:30,190
Well, uh, That would be the captain
of our ship, Lady Alvida, of course.

30
00:03:29,190 --> 00:03:30,480
[ALVIDA chuckles]

31
00:03:30,480 --> 00:03:34,490
[laughing]

32
00:03:36,820 --> 00:03:37,820
Good answer.

33
00:03:37,820 --> 00:03:39,740
That means a lot to me.

34
00:03:39,740 --> 00:03:40,990
It's been a while...

35
00:03:40,990 --> 00:03:42,950
We're finally gonna see a little action.

36
00:03:42,950 --> 00:03:43,540
That's right!

37
00:03:44,330 --> 00:03:48,000
So make it count!
Hit 'em with all you got, boys!

38
00:03:46,500 --> 00:03:49,500
[PIRATES cheering]

39
00:03:54,960 --> 00:03:57,930
[PASSENGERS screaming]

40
00:04:08,310 --> 00:04:09,850
[PIRATES grunt]

41
00:04:12,020 --> 00:04:13,020
Here we go!

42
00:04:13,020 --> 00:04:15,650
Time to show them
the terror of Iron Club Alvida,

43
00:04:15,650 --> 00:04:17,320
Lady Pirate of the Seas!

44
00:04:17,900 --> 00:04:20,280
[PIRATES yelling]

45
00:04:20,780 --> 00:04:26,410
[yelling continues]

46
00:04:26,410 --> 00:04:27,830
[whimpering]

47
00:04:27,830 --> 00:04:30,040
Koby! What are you doing?!

48
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:32,290
I'm not... real good at this stuff.

49
00:04:32,290 --> 00:04:33,540
[scoffs] You're telling me.

50
00:04:33,540 --> 00:04:36,210
Maybe it's 'cause you're too busy
back-talking me all the time.

51
00:04:36,210 --> 00:04:38,930
Oh no! Not the club!
Anything but the club!

52
00:04:38,930 --> 00:04:40,840
Please!

53
00:04:40,840 --> 00:04:42,510
Then get your ass in gear!

54
00:04:42,510 --> 00:04:44,430
[screams]

55
00:04:47,100 --> 00:04:48,560
[sobbing]

56
00:04:48,560 --> 00:04:50,850
[ALVIDA] Move it, you brat!

57
00:04:49,270 --> 00:04:50,850
[KOBY gasps]

58
00:04:50,850 --> 00:04:53,310
[ALVIDA yelling]

59
00:04:53,560 --> 00:04:55,230
[screaming]

60
00:05:00,200 --> 00:05:01,240
[ALVIDA groans]

61
00:05:01,740 --> 00:05:04,200
[PIRATES laughing]

62
00:05:04,580 --> 00:05:07,200
We're not gonna
take your lives, we swear...

63
00:05:07,200 --> 00:05:09,660
But we will take
everything else you got on ya.

64
00:05:09,660 --> 00:05:14,420
[ALVIDA]
And anyone who fights back will be eating
their dinner off the bottom of the ocean.

65
00:05:14,750 --> 00:05:16,500
[KOBY]
Uh, hello...?

66
00:05:18,630 --> 00:05:20,840
I really hope there's no one in here.

67
00:05:21,970 --> 00:05:23,970
[sighs] That's a relief...

68
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:25,510
Hm?

69
00:05:26,760 --> 00:05:28,520
[KOBY]
Wow, that's one big barrel.

70
00:05:28,520 --> 00:05:29,930
I wonder what's inside of it.

71
00:05:30,430 --> 00:05:36,110
[KOBY groaning]

72
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:36,110
[apprehensive music]

73
00:05:36,110 --> 00:05:37,940
It's our favorite coward.

74
00:05:37,940 --> 00:05:40,780
You trying to hide in here
and duck out on all the action again?

75
00:05:40,780 --> 00:05:41,700
No way!

76
00:05:41,700 --> 00:05:44,450
I was just trying to haul this
big barrel of beer over to you guys!

77
00:05:44,450 --> 00:05:45,950
[laughs]

78
00:05:45,950 --> 00:05:47,950
Why don't you let us
lighten your load?

79
00:05:47,950 --> 00:05:49,450
[PIRATE B]
I was just startin' to get thirsty.

80
00:05:49,450 --> 00:05:50,580
You can't!

81
00:05:50,580 --> 00:05:52,920
Lady Alvida will kill us
if she ever found out!

82
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:55,670
She won't if you keep your trap shut.

83
00:05:55,670 --> 00:05:57,420
Right.. boy?

84
00:05:57,420 --> 00:05:59,170
Yeah... Right.

85
00:05:59,170 --> 00:06:00,880
[laughs nervously] Okay.

86
00:06:00,880 --> 00:06:02,170
This sucker's heavy.

87
00:06:02,170 --> 00:06:03,340
[PIRATE B]
Hah, perfect.

88
00:06:03,340 --> 00:06:05,470
[PIRATE A]
I'll open her the old fashioned way.

89
00:06:05,470 --> 00:06:06,390
[PIRATE A growls]

90
00:06:07,260 --> 00:06:08,310
[growling continues]

91
00:06:08,310 --> 00:06:14,690
[LUFFY yelling]

92
00:06:09,270 --> 00:06:12,730
[ALL scream]

93
00:06:09,770 --> 00:06:12,730
[triumphant orchestral music]

94
00:06:14,690 --> 00:06:16,650
[LUFFY]
I...

95
00:06:16,650 --> 00:06:18,480
slept...

96
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:21,440
so...

97
00:06:21,440 --> 00:06:24,700
great...!

98
00:06:22,070 --> 00:06:23,070
[thunk]

99
00:06:24,700 --> 00:06:25,410
Hm?

100
00:06:25,410 --> 00:06:26,620
Who's that?

101
00:06:30,870 --> 00:06:31,750
Who the hell are you guys?

102
00:06:31,750 --> 00:06:33,620
Who the hell are you?!

103
00:06:33,620 --> 00:06:35,750
Your friend will catch cold
sleeping like that.

104
00:06:35,750 --> 00:06:37,460
You're the one who knocked him out!

105
00:06:38,390 --> 00:06:38,880
[LUFFY]
Hm?

106
00:06:38,880 --> 00:06:40,130
Hold up!

107
00:06:40,130 --> 00:06:43,970
Are you messing with us when you know
good and well that we're vicious pirates?! Huh?!

108
00:06:43,970 --> 00:06:45,180
– [KOBY gasps]
– [LUFFY] I'm starving.

109
00:06:45,180 --> 00:06:46,340
[LUFFY]
You got any food?

110
00:06:45,890 --> 00:06:47,930
I'm talking to you!

111
00:06:48,260 --> 00:06:49,680
[growls] You damn kid!

112
00:06:49,680 --> 00:06:52,680
[PIRATES yelling]

113
00:06:50,430 --> 00:06:51,770
[KOBY screams]

114
00:06:51,770 --> 00:06:52,680
[LUFFY] Hm?

115
00:06:52,680 --> 00:06:55,140
[PIRATES growl] Die!

116
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:55,140
[KOBY whimpers]

117
00:06:55,650 --> 00:06:56,060
[metal clangs]

118
00:07:04,320 --> 00:07:06,160
[KOBY whimpers, gasps]

119
00:06:56,060 --> 00:06:57,150
[PIRATES gasp]

120
00:07:10,530 --> 00:07:12,500
What is wrong with you two?

121
00:07:12,500 --> 00:07:14,830
[PIRATE C]
Wh-Who are you?!

122
00:07:14,830 --> 00:07:16,420
[LUFFY]
Me? Oh...

123
00:07:16,960 --> 00:07:18,830
My name's Monkey D. Luffy.

124
00:07:18,830 --> 00:07:20,670
Hi! [laughs]

125
00:07:20,670 --> 00:07:23,590
[PIRATES screaming]

126
00:07:27,800 --> 00:07:29,890
So... what just happened?

127
00:07:29,890 --> 00:07:30,850
You got me.

128
00:07:30,850 --> 00:07:32,770
[gasps] Quick! You've gotta run!

129
00:07:32,770 --> 00:07:36,270
If those guys come back here with
their buddies, then they'll kill you on the spot!

130
00:07:36,270 --> 00:07:38,020
I don't care about that. I'm hungry.

131
00:07:38,020 --> 00:07:40,270
How can you just blow
this off like that?!

132
00:07:40,270 --> 00:07:41,650
There are hundreds
of them up on deck

133
00:07:41,650 --> 00:07:44,280
and they're waiting for
the opportunity to kill anything!

134
00:07:44,280 --> 00:07:45,110
[LUFFY grunting]

135
00:07:45,110 --> 00:07:45,820
[KOBY straining]

136
00:07:45,820 --> 00:07:48,820
[KOBY mumbling]
You're going the wrong way!

137
00:07:50,320 --> 00:07:51,990
No! Wait!

138
00:07:51,990 --> 00:07:54,160
[LUFFY growling]

139
00:07:54,160 --> 00:07:54,750
[shrieks]

140
00:07:54,750 --> 00:07:56,710
[laughs]

141
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:58,670
It's a gold mine!

142
00:07:58,670 --> 00:08:00,170
Food! Food! Food! Food! Food!

143
00:08:00,170 --> 00:08:01,040
[KOBY]
Who's knows...

144
00:08:00,540 --> 00:08:01,980
[LUFFY laughs]

145
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:04,670
[KOBY]
Maybe we'll be safe in here
as long as no one else gets hungry.

146
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:05,800
[LUFFY]
Ooh, which one should I take first?
This box looks promising!

147
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:08,630
[LUFFY]
Apples! Excellent! [laughs]

148
00:08:08,630 --> 00:08:10,390
Heh, tasty!

149
00:08:10,390 --> 00:08:13,010
[KOBY]
Uh... Hey! My name's Koby!

150
00:08:13,010 --> 00:08:14,770
You're Luffy. Is that right?

151
00:08:14,770 --> 00:08:17,640
That was pretty neat when you
jumped out of that barrel back there.

152
00:08:18,390 --> 00:08:19,600
These are awesome!

153
00:08:19,980 --> 00:08:20,770
[KOBY laughs nervously]

154
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:23,440
[LUFFY]
So are we on a pirate ship or what?

155
00:08:23,440 --> 00:08:24,110
[KOBY]
No...

156
00:08:24,110 --> 00:08:26,940
It's a passenger ship
that's being raided by pirates,

157
00:08:26,940 --> 00:08:29,490
pirates under the command
of Lady Alvida.

158
00:08:29,490 --> 00:08:30,740
[LUFFY]
Aw, who cares anyway?

159
00:08:30,740 --> 00:08:33,620
What I wanna know is if
there are any boats on board.

160
00:08:33,620 --> 00:08:35,330
[KOBY]
I think there are a few.

161
00:08:35,330 --> 00:08:38,120
[LUFFY]
Great! 'Cause mine got sucked
into some big whirlpool.

162
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:40,710
[KOBY]
That one outside? No way!

163
00:08:40,710 --> 00:08:42,590
No one could have survived that.

164
00:08:42,590 --> 00:08:46,050
[laughs] Yeah! I gotta say,
it was a big surprise!

165
00:08:46,050 --> 00:08:47,170
[laughs nervously]

166
00:08:47,170 --> 00:08:49,760
[LUFFY]
So are you one of the pirates
or one of the passengers?

167
00:08:49,760 --> 00:08:50,720
[KOBY gasps]

168
00:08:53,800 --> 00:08:56,970
It was on a fateful day, long ago...

169
00:08:57,600 --> 00:08:58,730
That day...

170
00:08:58,730 --> 00:09:00,600
I stepped out onto
a small fishing boat

171
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:02,940
on the outskirts of town
to go catch my dinner.

172
00:09:04,820 --> 00:09:05,400
[KOBY]
Huh?

173
00:09:07,400 --> 00:09:08,190
[whimpers]

174
00:09:08,190 --> 00:09:12,320
[KOBY]
Turned out that particular boat
was actually headed for a pirate ship.

175
00:09:12,320 --> 00:09:14,080
That was two years ago.

176
00:09:14,700 --> 00:09:16,830
In exchange for them letting me live,

177
00:09:16,830 --> 00:09:19,790
I'm forced to live
the life of a cabin boy.

178
00:09:21,080 --> 00:09:23,080
[LUFFY]
You're pretty stupid, you know that?

179
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:25,250
[KOBY]
Gee, thanks for your honesty.

180
00:09:25,250 --> 00:09:26,500
[LUFFY]
If you hate it, then leave.

181
00:09:26,500 --> 00:09:28,010
[KOBY]
Are you kidding?! I can't do that!

182
00:09:28,010 --> 00:09:29,880
No way! Nuh-uh! Not a chance!

183
00:09:29,880 --> 00:09:33,050
Just the thought of Alvida finding me
scares me so bad, I wanna throw up!

184
00:09:33,050 --> 00:09:35,390
[laughing] You're a moron
and a coward!

185
00:09:35,390 --> 00:09:38,060
[laughing] I hate people like you!

186
00:09:38,060 --> 00:09:40,020
– [LUFFY laughing]
– [KOBY sobs]

187
00:09:39,020 --> 00:09:40,520
[menacing orchestral music]

188
00:09:40,520 --> 00:09:43,150
All right, quit your
lollygagging around, boys!

189
00:09:43,150 --> 00:09:46,020
We gotta load up everything
before the Marines get here.

190
00:09:46,940 --> 00:09:50,950
I catch anyone dawdling, and they'll
get a real mouthful of my iron club!

191
00:09:54,620 --> 00:09:56,870
[PIRATES screaming]

192
00:09:56,870 --> 00:09:58,080
[BOTH]
Captain!

193
00:09:58,410 --> 00:09:59,120
[ALVIDA growls]

194
00:09:59,120 --> 00:10:00,040
[PIRATE B & C]
This is bad!

195
00:10:00,410 --> 00:10:01,870
[ALVIDA]
Yeah...? Then out with it!

196
00:10:01,870 --> 00:10:03,540
[PIRATE C]
It came from inside the barrel!

197
00:10:03,540 --> 00:10:05,540
[PIRATE B]
Such a horrible monster!

198
00:10:05,540 --> 00:10:06,460
[ALVIDA growls]
Huh?

199
00:10:06,460 --> 00:10:07,960
[PIRATES whimper]

200
00:10:08,420 --> 00:10:10,420
[ALVIDA grunts]
Who are you...

201
00:10:10,420 --> 00:10:11,170
[PIRATES scream]

202
00:10:11,170 --> 00:10:12,880
[ALVIDA]
...calling a monster?!

203
00:10:11,970 --> 00:10:14,220
[PIRATE A screaming]

204
00:10:17,930 --> 00:10:22,640
Uh... we weren't... talkin'...
about... you, my lady.

205
00:10:22,640 --> 00:10:25,150
Some guy was hiding in a barrel!

206
00:10:25,150 --> 00:10:26,690
He could be a bounty hunter!

207
00:10:26,690 --> 00:10:27,940
What?!

208
00:10:28,980 --> 00:10:30,320
Yeah, you're right.

209
00:10:30,320 --> 00:10:32,070
If I had the courage,

210
00:10:32,070 --> 00:10:34,450
I could drift alone in a barrel
and be rid of these pirates.

211
00:10:34,450 --> 00:10:36,570
I actually have my own dreams.

212
00:10:36,570 --> 00:10:39,490
Someday... I'd like
to live out all of them.

213
00:10:40,330 --> 00:10:42,080
So, what about you, Luffy?

214
00:10:42,080 --> 00:10:44,750
What was it that first got you
to set sail on these seas?

215
00:10:44,750 --> 00:10:45,290
[LUFFY]
Hm?

216
00:10:45,790 --> 00:10:49,380
[laughs] Well, I'm gonna be
King of the Pirates!

217
00:10:49,380 --> 00:10:51,590
[gasping]

218
00:10:51,590 --> 00:10:52,340
The King?!

219
00:10:52,340 --> 00:10:52,760
Yep.

220
00:10:52,760 --> 00:10:53,840
Are you serious?!

221
00:10:53,840 --> 00:10:54,470
Yeah!

222
00:10:54,470 --> 00:10:57,260
But... But that would mean
that you're a pirate, too!

223
00:10:57,260 --> 00:10:58,010
Right.

224
00:10:58,600 --> 00:10:59,100
Your crew?

225
00:10:59,100 --> 00:11:01,100
Don't have one yet,
but I'm lookin' for 'em.

226
00:11:01,100 --> 00:11:03,020
[KOBY gasps]

227
00:11:03,020 --> 00:11:03,680
[LUFFY]
Hm?

228
00:11:06,690 --> 00:11:09,650
[yelps] King of the Pirates
is a title given to one

229
00:11:09,650 --> 00:11:11,980
who obtains everything
this world has to offer!

230
00:11:11,980 --> 00:11:15,910
You're talking about seeking the great
treasure of wealth, fame, and power!

231
00:11:15,910 --> 00:11:18,570
The treasure that you
seek is the One Piece!

232
00:11:18,570 --> 00:11:19,160
Yeah!

233
00:11:19,160 --> 00:11:20,410
Yeah?! That's it?!

234
00:11:20,410 --> 00:11:23,540
Pirates from all over the world are
looking for that treasure, ya know?!

235
00:11:23,540 --> 00:11:24,580
Yeah? So?

236
00:11:24,580 --> 00:11:27,080
No way! It's impossible,
impossible, impossible!

237
00:11:27,080 --> 00:11:30,590
There's no way anyone like you could ever
reach the pinnacle during this Great Pirate Age!

238
00:11:30,590 --> 00:11:33,590
There's just too many out there
that are meaner and better!

239
00:11:34,760 --> 00:11:37,640
[KOBY]
Ow... Why did you hit me?

240
00:11:37,640 --> 00:11:38,890
'Cause I felt like it.

241
00:11:38,890 --> 00:11:40,260
[KOBY groans]

242
00:11:40,260 --> 00:11:42,890
Oh, well... I'm used to that stuff...

243
00:11:42,890 --> 00:11:45,020
My shipmates smack me
around a lot...

244
00:11:45,020 --> 00:11:46,230
all the time, in fact.

245
00:11:46,230 --> 00:11:48,100
[LUFFY]
It's not about if I can.

246
00:11:48,100 --> 00:11:48,730
[KOBY]
Huh?

247
00:11:48,730 --> 00:11:50,400
[LUFFY]
I'm doing this 'cause I want to.

248
00:11:52,980 --> 00:11:56,740
I decided long ago that
I'm gonna be King of the Pirates.

249
00:11:56,740 --> 00:11:59,950
If I have to die fighting
for that... then I die.

250
00:11:59,950 --> 00:12:02,950
[KOBY gasping]

251
00:12:02,950 --> 00:12:03,950
All right...

252
00:12:03,950 --> 00:12:07,620
Now that my belly's full, I'm gonna
go get me a brand new boat.

253
00:12:07,620 --> 00:12:10,040
They might even just give me
one if I ask nice enough.

254
00:12:10,040 --> 00:12:12,040
Maybe they're generous people.

255
00:12:12,040 --> 00:12:14,670
[KOBY]
I guess I never thought of it like that.

256
00:12:14,670 --> 00:12:18,840
[soft piano music]

257
00:12:15,380 --> 00:12:18,840
If I put my mind to it,
if I'm prepared to die for it,

258
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:20,890
could I do something like that?

259
00:12:20,890 --> 00:12:21,720
Like what?

260
00:12:22,390 --> 00:12:23,390
Do you think...?

261
00:12:24,010 --> 00:12:26,390
Do you think I could
ever join the Marines?

262
00:12:27,100 --> 00:12:27,940
[LUFFY]
Marines?

263
00:12:27,940 --> 00:12:31,730
Yes! Catching bad guys is
the only thing I've ever wanted to do!

264
00:12:31,730 --> 00:12:34,190
It's been my dream
since I was a child!

265
00:12:34,190 --> 00:12:35,940
Do you think I can do it?

266
00:12:35,940 --> 00:12:37,070
[LUFFY]
How should I know that?

267
00:12:37,070 --> 00:12:38,490
[KOBY]
Then I'm gonna do it!

268
00:12:38,490 --> 00:12:41,820
I'm not gonna get stuck here
as a cabin boy for the rest of my life!

269
00:12:41,820 --> 00:12:45,200
I'll break out, then I'll turn right
around, and catch Alvida myself!

270
00:12:46,660 --> 00:12:50,960
[KOBY screaming]

271
00:12:50,000 --> 00:12:54,420
[menacing music]

272
00:12:52,000 --> 00:12:54,420
[ALVIDA]
Who is that you
plan on catching, Koby?

273
00:12:54,420 --> 00:12:57,340
And you actually think
this twig is gonna help you?

274
00:12:57,340 --> 00:12:57,970
Well?

275
00:12:57,970 --> 00:13:02,050
[KOBY whimpering]

276
00:12:58,630 --> 00:13:00,380
[ALVIDA] Answer me!

277
00:13:02,050 --> 00:13:03,890
[ALVIDA growls]

278
00:13:03,890 --> 00:13:06,020
[KOBY whimpering]

279
00:13:12,860 --> 00:13:13,900
[ALVIDA chuckles]

280
00:13:13,900 --> 00:13:16,400
My guess is that you're
not Zoro, the Pirate Hunter.

281
00:13:16,400 --> 00:13:17,400
[KOBY gasps]

282
00:13:17,400 --> 00:13:18,110
[LUFFY]
Zoro?

283
00:13:18,110 --> 00:13:19,110
[ALVIDA]
Koby!

284
00:13:19,110 --> 00:13:19,860
[shrieks]

285
00:13:19,320 --> 00:13:23,120
[ALVIDA]
Who is most beautiful of all
on these seas?

286
00:13:23,120 --> 00:13:25,330
[KOBY stammers]
Well... I... Um...

287
00:13:25,330 --> 00:13:27,290
G-Give me a sec... I know this...

288
00:13:27,910 --> 00:13:29,750
Hey, Koby, who's the fat lady?

289
00:13:34,750 --> 00:13:36,250
[PIRATES whimpering]

290
00:13:36,250 --> 00:13:37,210
Oh no...

291
00:13:37,210 --> 00:13:38,170
Not good...

292
00:13:38,170 --> 00:13:40,970
[ALVIDA growling]

293
00:13:40,970 --> 00:13:42,180
You...

294
00:13:42,180 --> 00:13:44,140
runt!

295
00:13:45,100 --> 00:13:47,100
[KOBY whimpers]

296
00:13:47,100 --> 00:13:47,720
[LUFFY]
Let's go.

297
00:13:47,720 --> 00:13:48,060
[KOBY]
Huh?

298
00:13:49,060 --> 00:13:50,600
[KOBY screaming]

299
00:13:49,060 --> 00:13:50,600
[energetic orchestral music]

300
00:13:51,060 --> 00:13:53,270
[PIRATES gasping]

301
00:13:54,770 --> 00:13:55,730
[LUFFY laughs]

302
00:13:56,070 --> 00:13:56,900
[PIRATE growling]

303
00:14:04,370 --> 00:14:06,330
Missed me!

304
00:14:11,460 --> 00:14:13,000
[LUFFY laughs]

305
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:14,170
[KOBY sighs]

306
00:14:14,170 --> 00:14:14,790
[screams]

307
00:14:18,130 --> 00:14:20,840
[LUFFY]
It's not fair to attack from behind.

308
00:14:20,840 --> 00:14:24,510
[PIRATES screaming]

309
00:14:25,680 --> 00:14:26,350
[LUFFY]
Hm?

310
00:14:28,310 --> 00:14:32,980
[screams] And it's even more not fair
to gang up on a guy!

311
00:14:40,900 --> 00:14:42,400
[PIRATES screaming]

312
00:14:42,400 --> 00:14:43,280
Gotcha!

313
00:14:45,160 --> 00:14:46,450
[LUFFY]
Gum...

314
00:14:46,780 --> 00:14:50,410
Gum...

315
00:14:50,410 --> 00:14:51,080
[ALVIDA growls]

316
00:14:51,910 --> 00:14:54,210
[LUFFY]
Rocket!

317
00:14:56,170 --> 00:14:58,750
[gasping]

318
00:15:01,170 --> 00:15:04,010
– [PIRATES moaning]
– [footsteps]

319
00:15:04,010 --> 00:15:05,300
[KOBY]
Luffy...

320
00:15:05,300 --> 00:15:06,260
What are you?

321
00:15:06,260 --> 00:15:06,720
[LUFFY]
Oh...

322
00:15:07,050 --> 00:15:09,180
[laughs] I'm a rubber man.

323
00:15:09,720 --> 00:15:12,430
So you're... made of rubber...?

324
00:15:12,430 --> 00:15:13,060
I...

325
00:15:13,060 --> 00:15:13,680
[gasps]

326
00:15:13,680 --> 00:15:15,560
[KOBY screams]

327
00:15:16,770 --> 00:15:19,440
So, you've eaten of the devil fruits.

328
00:15:20,190 --> 00:15:22,280
Yeah. I ate the Gum-Gum one.

329
00:15:22,280 --> 00:15:24,280
[apprehensive string music]

330
00:15:22,280 --> 00:15:24,280
Ah-ha...

331
00:15:24,280 --> 00:15:26,110
I heard rumors they existed,

332
00:15:26,110 --> 00:15:29,490
but I'd never seen any evidence
of them before today.

333
00:15:29,490 --> 00:15:32,290
You're more skilled than
the average deck swabber.

334
00:15:32,290 --> 00:15:33,410
Are you a bounty hunter?

335
00:15:33,410 --> 00:15:35,210
[LUFFY]
I'm a pirate!

336
00:15:35,210 --> 00:15:36,500
Pirate? Ha!

337
00:15:36,500 --> 00:15:38,460
All by yourself on these waters?

338
00:15:38,460 --> 00:15:39,670
[LUFFY]
Today, it's just me.

339
00:15:39,670 --> 00:15:42,550
But I'll find my crew tomorrow
or next week or something.

340
00:15:42,550 --> 00:15:43,800
I need... ten guys.

341
00:15:43,800 --> 00:15:44,470
[ALVIDA]
Hah!

342
00:15:45,800 --> 00:15:47,470
[ALVIDA]
That would make us enemies.

343
00:15:47,470 --> 00:15:48,640
Am I right?

344
00:15:48,640 --> 00:15:50,800
[whispers] Uh, Luffy? Let's go.

345
00:15:50,800 --> 00:15:51,310
But why?

346
00:15:51,310 --> 00:15:53,470
You saw how powerful her club is.

347
00:15:53,470 --> 00:15:57,140
And of all the villainous cheats in all
these waters, she's easily the most...

348
00:15:59,400 --> 00:16:02,900
I decided long ago that I'm
gonna be King of the Pirates.

349
00:16:02,900 --> 00:16:06,070
If I have to die fighting
for that... then I die.

350
00:16:09,070 --> 00:16:10,950
Go on...

351
00:16:10,950 --> 00:16:11,870
Tell me...

352
00:16:11,870 --> 00:16:14,620
[KOBY whimpering]

353
00:16:15,500 --> 00:16:16,370
You're the most...

354
00:16:16,370 --> 00:16:18,500
ugliest thing on the sea!

355
00:16:22,750 --> 00:16:26,720
[ALVIDA growling]

356
00:16:26,720 --> 00:16:29,470
[KOBY whimpering]

357
00:16:29,470 --> 00:16:33,680
[laughing]

358
00:16:33,680 --> 00:16:35,140
What'd you say?!

359
00:16:35,140 --> 00:16:35,770
[laughing continues]

360
00:16:35,770 --> 00:16:38,060
[KOBY]
I'm leaving and I'm gonna
join the Marines!

361
00:16:38,060 --> 00:16:41,150
Then I'm gonna spend the rest of my
life beating up dirty pirates like you!

362
00:16:41,150 --> 00:16:43,400
[ALVIDA]
Do you have any clue what you're
saying to me right now?!

363
00:16:43,400 --> 00:16:44,360
[KOBY]
Of course I do!

364
00:16:44,360 --> 00:16:46,860
And I'm gonna do what I want,
and no one's gonna stop me!

365
00:16:46,860 --> 00:16:49,150
And when I join the Marines,
I'm gonna join them!

366
00:16:49,450 --> 00:16:51,820
And I'm gonna catch
your lousy ass first!

367
00:16:51,820 --> 00:16:52,910
You're dead, kid!

368
00:16:53,240 --> 00:16:53,990
[ALVIDA yelling]

369
00:16:53,990 --> 00:16:55,700
[KOBY]
No regrets! No regrets!

370
00:16:55,700 --> 00:16:59,210
I did it! I said what I wanted to
and I fought for my dream!

371
00:16:59,210 --> 00:17:00,460
Well said! [laughs]

372
00:17:00,460 --> 00:17:01,960
[yells]

373
00:17:12,510 --> 00:17:14,350
Heh. That won't work.

374
00:17:14,350 --> 00:17:15,310
What?!

375
00:17:15,310 --> 00:17:16,310
[LUFFY]
I'm rubber!

376
00:17:20,560 --> 00:17:21,440
[LUFFY]
Gum...

377
00:17:21,770 --> 00:17:24,360
Gum...

378
00:17:24,770 --> 00:17:25,650
Hah!

379
00:17:25,650 --> 00:17:27,940
...Pistol!

380
00:17:32,240 --> 00:17:36,410
[ALVIDA screaming]

381
00:17:48,050 --> 00:17:50,800
[PIRATE A]
The sky's so pretty and blue out here.

382
00:17:52,130 --> 00:17:52,680
Huh?

383
00:18:02,480 --> 00:18:03,520
[LUFFY]
Hey, you!

384
00:18:03,520 --> 00:18:04,400
[PIRATES]
Yes?!

385
00:18:04,400 --> 00:18:07,110
Go find a boat and give it to Koby.

386
00:18:07,110 --> 00:18:09,360
He's leaving your ship
to join the Marines.

387
00:18:09,360 --> 00:18:10,690
You're not gonna stop him.

388
00:18:10,690 --> 00:18:13,160
[PIRATES]
Uh... Yeah, sure!

389
00:18:13,570 --> 00:18:16,200
[KOBY gasps]
Thanks, Luffy.

390
00:18:19,620 --> 00:18:22,120
[BOTH screaming]

391
00:18:22,120 --> 00:18:22,540
[BOTH gasp]

392
00:18:23,040 --> 00:18:25,040
[KOBY]
Look! It's the Marines!

393
00:18:25,040 --> 00:18:26,340
[LUFFY]
Ooh!

394
00:18:26,340 --> 00:18:27,460
Perfect timing!

395
00:18:27,460 --> 00:18:29,340
Head over there
and tell 'em you wanna join.

396
00:18:29,340 --> 00:18:29,630
[KOBY]
Huh?

397
00:18:29,630 --> 00:18:31,340
[LUFFY]
But I'm a pirate, so I'm outta here!

398
00:18:31,340 --> 00:18:33,090
No, wait! You can't be serious!

399
00:18:33,090 --> 00:18:36,050
I approach them like this, they'll just
capture me like another pirate!

400
00:18:48,650 --> 00:18:50,940
[KOBY]
We actually managed to get away!

401
00:18:50,940 --> 00:18:52,990
[sighs] What fun!

402
00:18:52,990 --> 00:18:54,320
[laughing]

403
00:18:54,320 --> 00:18:55,820
So, Luffy.

404
00:18:55,820 --> 00:18:56,450
[LUFFY]
Huh?

405
00:18:56,450 --> 00:18:58,700
If you're searching for
the elusive One Piece,

406
00:18:58,700 --> 00:19:01,330
then you have to be headed
for the Grand Line, right?

407
00:19:01,330 --> 00:19:01,830
[LUFFY]
Mm-hmm.

408
00:19:01,830 --> 00:19:05,080
You know, the people I've talked to
call that place the pirate graveyard.

409
00:19:05,080 --> 00:19:07,790
Right. And that's why I need
an extra-strong crew.

410
00:19:08,290 --> 00:19:10,300
You guys mentioned
some pirate hunter.

411
00:19:10,300 --> 00:19:11,630
So what's he like, Koby?

412
00:19:12,210 --> 00:19:13,720
Oh, you mean Zoro?

413
00:19:13,720 --> 00:19:17,390
Last I heard was that he's being
held prisoner at some Marine base.

414
00:19:17,390 --> 00:19:18,260
Oh, well...

415
00:19:18,260 --> 00:19:19,300
A weakling, huh?

416
00:19:19,300 --> 00:19:20,640
No, you're so wrong!

417
00:19:20,640 --> 00:19:24,350
He's as violent as a demon,
and three times as horrifying!

418
00:19:25,390 --> 00:19:27,730
Why are you asking
about him anyway?

419
00:19:27,730 --> 00:19:31,690
[giggles] I figure if he's good enough,
I'd ask him to join my crew!

420
00:19:32,650 --> 00:19:35,150
[KOBY]
Chasing him down
is just plain reckless!

421
00:19:35,150 --> 00:19:37,410
[LUFFY]
You never know! He might jump
at the chance to join me!

422
00:19:37,410 --> 00:19:39,660
[KOBY]
He's a bad enough guy
that the Marines caught him!

423
00:19:39,660 --> 00:19:41,160
No way! Not a chance!

424
00:19:41,160 --> 00:19:41,990
Forget it! No, no–

425
00:19:41,990 --> 00:19:42,330
[thud]

426
00:19:42,330 --> 00:19:43,370
Ow!

427
00:19:43,370 --> 00:19:45,370
[groans] Why'd you hit me?

428
00:19:45,370 --> 00:19:46,620
[LUFFY]
'Cause I felt like it.

429
00:03:20,930 --> 00:03:25,640
Cabin Boy Koby

430
00:03:20,930 --> 00:03:25,640
Cabin Boy Koby

431
00:03:35,570 --> 00:03:39,780
The Lady Pirate, "Iron Club" Alvida

432
00:03:35,570 --> 00:03:39,780
The Lady Pirate, "Iron Club" Alvida

433
00:03:35,570 --> 00:03:39,780
The Lady Pirate, "Iron Club" Alvida
